data.description: Quiet and Peaceful Home on Acreage. This single level 3 bdrm 2 bath home (built in 2005) sits on a level and wooded .87 acre lot with no CCRs. 1404 sqft of clean & tidy living space with a 2 car garage. The expansive front and back yards are fully fenced with a raised bed garden area. The entire lot includes the open acreage to the north. As you arrive at your new house follow the covered sidewalk from the driveway to your covered front patio. Enter into the open concept living area with vaulted ceilings, natural gas fireplace, and views too your natural setting in the backyard. Dining room features french doors to the covered back deck and woodland views. The modern kitchen offers a breakfast bar, pantry storage, and stainless appliances; new stainless microwave and new hot water heater. Laminate flooring throughout. Private primary suite enjoys a private bath and walk in closet. Natural gas stove for efficient heating, community water, and high speed internet, on a short private road. Find your peace and quiet among the pines in this move in ready home in a great location.
